</p></li></ul></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_44E3E3F07D374BF6964EC50817FE9018" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_81211933FE8E4F0882F506D037CBF8F4" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T10 
</p></li><li id="LI_52DBF4023EA944F89CD5A1B41DA11017" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-D89CA596-85C0-4E9F-B3A9-999BF9C916D2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="FIG_09D69A8F96914C4B91FA6B9BD4DF96DC" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-18DF1DCE-B6A0-4D45-A866-469963019427-low.png" id="IMAGE_3380D77C0CB54275A14CD64158FC1732" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-18DF1DCE-B6A0-4D45-A866-469963019427-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_9EC224F88E8A4080AE56B56A407D1992" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-41BD20B8-4B2F-4FEC-8C34-8F26D7993B2A-low.png" id="IMAGE_47397CE0E9CC4B7894F445B2B47BB14B" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-41BD20B8-4B2F-4FEC-8C34-8F26D7993B2A-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_7BCF39D178844448B3A21E7E56376710" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table id="TABLE_5FBEFB7447DE4A1D819BDF873A72E3DB" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
